<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Penitent" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Penitent,</orth> 1) repentant: <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. V, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 4.2.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 2, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.480.53" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 480</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.2.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 2, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.2.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 2, 7</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.4" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.1.27" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C V, 1, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.221" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 221</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.63" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 63</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.4.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 4, 10</bibl>. Substantively: <cit><quote>it was the desire of the p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 4.2.188" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 2, 188</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thy p. reformed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.239" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 239</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I'll play the p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 2.2.92" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 2, 92</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) doing penance: <cit><quote>we that know what 'tis to fast and pray are p. for your default to-day,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 1.2.52" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 2, 52</bibl></cit>. Substantively: <cit><quote>of enjoined --s there's four or five, to great Saint Jaques bound,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 3.5.97" default="NO" valid="yes">All's III, 5, 97</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>